Helium framework

an MVC framework for PHP

inspired by rails, a bit.
snatched the inflector code from rails too.

/
-- htdocs/ (or htdocs)
---- .htaccess		# preset to get the engine running
---- index.php		# include()s helium.php
-- conf/
----- conf.php 		# main configuration file
----- db.php		# database configuration file (optional)
----- routes.php	# routes configuration file
-- helium.php		# the heart
-- lib/ 			# class etc. that keep helium running
etc...